snippet: Joey Logano improved his chances of reaching the Chase for the Sprint Cup, edging Kevin Harvick by one second at Michigan International Speedway.
abstract: Joey Logano improves his chances of reaching Nascar's Chase for the Sprint Cup, edging Kevin Harvick by one second at Michigan International Speedway.
